# MSG-BACKEND-030 — Q3 Track A Quote Request API (PARTIAL DONE)

## Összefoglaló

✅ **Phase 1-2 COMPLETE** — API endpoint structure és domain logic alapok kész.

❌ **Phase 3-4-5 PENDING** — Migration, persistence, testing, rate limiting még hiányzik.

## Implementált komponensek

### 1. API Layer ✅

**Fájlok:**
- `SpaceOS.Modules.Cutting.Api/Endpoints/QuoteRequestEndpoints.cs` (updated)
  - Új endpoint mapping: `POST /api/public/cutting/quote-request`
  - Handler method: `CreatePublicQuoteRequest()`
  - Error handling (400, 201, 500)

### 2. Application Layer ✅

**DTO-k:**
- `Application/DTOs/QuoteRequest/PublicQuoteRequestDto.cs` (new)
  - PublicQuoteRequestDto (Data Annotations validation)
  - DimensionsDto (mm validáció: 1-10000 length/width, 1-500 thickness)
  - AttachmentDto (base64 support)
  - PublicQuoteResponseDto

**CQRS komponensek:**
- `Application/Commands/CreatePublicQuoteRequest/CreatePublicQuoteRequestCommand.cs` (new)
- `Application/Commands/CreatePublicQuoteRequest/CreatePublicQuoteRequestCommandHandler.cs` (new)
  - Entitás létrehozás logic
  - Estimated reply time kalkuláció (standard: 2 business days, express: 1 day)
  - **NOTE:** Persistence commented out (migration hiányzik)

### 3. Domain Layer ✅

**Entitás:**
- `Domain/Entities/PublicQuoteRequest.cs` (new)
  - Flat entity structure (nem aggregate, nincs tenant ID)
  - Factory method: `Create()`
  - Status update method
  - Timestamps (CreatedAt, UpdatedAt)

### 4. Infrastructure Layer ✅

**DbContext:**
- `Infrastructure/Persistence/CuttingDbContext.cs` (updated)
  - `DbSet<PublicQuoteRequest> PublicQuoteRequests` hozzáadva

**EF Core Configuration:**
- `Infrastructure/Persistence/Configurations/PublicQuoteRequestConfiguration.cs` (new)
  - Table mapping: `spaceos_cutting.public_quote_requests`
  - Column mappings (max length, types, defaults)
  - Indexes:
    - customer_email
    - created_at (DESC)

